# KooliHub Color System

## Overview
Comprehensive color system with semantic colors, service-specific palettes, status colors, and theme support.

---

## 1. Color Architecture

### 1.1 Color Token Hierarchy
```
Colors
├── Primitive Colors (Raw Values)
│   ├── Brand Colors (Yellow, etc.)
│   └── Neutral Palette (Gray scale)
│
├── Semantic Colors (Purpose-Based)
│   ├── Primary / Secondary
│   ├── Background / Foreground
│   ├── Muted / Accent
│   └── Destructive / Success / Warning / Info
│
├── Service Colors (Domain-Specific)
│   ├── Grocery (Green)
│   ├── Trips (Blue)
│   ├── Handyman (Orange)
│   └── ... other services
│
└── Status Colors (State-Based)
    ├── Order Status
    ├── Payment Status
    └── Generic Status
```

